text: Yaqubabad () is a neighborhood in Orangi Town in Karachi, Sindh, Pakistan.Orangi Town - Government of Karachi There are several ethnic groups including Muhajirs, Sindhis, Kashmiris, Seraikis, Pakhtuns, Balochis, Memons, Bohras Ismailis, etc. ==References== == External links == * Karachi Website Category:Neighbourhoods of Karachi Category:Orangi Town
title: Yaqubabad, Karachi
